original_title: Timeline: The History of WWE – 2001 – As Told By Lisa Moretti
overview: The WWE began to see the marketability of its lady wrestlers as both performers and sex symbols in the last decade or so. And man, did we find someone who has some stuff to say about it!  Lisa Moretti had an incredibly successful run as the character “Ivory” on WWE television. Join her as she takes us back to 2001 and we will live one year in the world’s most storied wrestling federation through the eyes of a DIVA!
title: Timeline: The History of WWE – 2001 – As Told By Lisa Moretti
